In a #cocktail shaker{} filled with ice, shake the @cognac{45%ml}, @orange liqueur{15%ml}, and @fresh orange juice{30%ml}.
Strain into a large #old-fashioned glass{} over fresh ice. Top with the @ginger ale{90%ml}.
Place the @lime twist{} into the top center of the @orange wheel{} and float on top of the drink
